---
// Services / Pricing component
---

<section id="services" class="services" data-animate>
  <div class="services__container">
    <span class="services__overline">SERVICES</span>

    <h2 class="services__headline">Pick what fits today. Add what you need when you're ready.</h2>

    <p class="services__intro">
      Start with a site that gets you found and gets you called. Then add the helpers that pick up when you're busy doing your work — they answer the calls, take the bookings, and have leads ready for you at the end of the day.
    </p>

    <div class="services__grid">
      <!-- Card 1: Starter Site -->
      <div class="services__card" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0s">
        <h3 class="services__card-title">Starter Site</h3>
        <span class="services__badge services__badge--popular">For starting out</span>
        <ul class="services__features">
          <li>4–5 page custom website</li>
          <li>Mobile-optimized</li>
          <li>Google Business Profile integration</li>
          <li>Basic local SEO</li>
          <li>Click-to-call + contact form</li>
          <li>Live in 1 week</li>
          <li>Free Netlify hosting included</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Full Site -->
      <div class="services__card services__card--featured" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
        <h3 class="services__card-title">Full Site</h3>
        <span class="services__badge services__badge--included">For serious growth</span>
        <ul class="services__features">
          <li>Everything in Starter Site, plus:</li>
          <li>Callback automation included</li>
          <li>Google Maps + schema markup</li>
          <li>Simple lead tracking</li>
          <li>Live in 1 week</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Care Plan -->
      <div class="services__card" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
        <h3 class="services__card-title">Care Plan</h3>
        <span class="services__badge services__badge--care">Always-on support</span>
        <ul class="services__features">
          <li>Content updates</li>
          <li>Uptime monitoring</li>
          <li>Form testing</li>
          <li>Google review link management</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="services__tagline">
          Your website works while you sleep. I make sure it stays that way.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="services__scope" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.3s">
      <p class="services__scope-text">
        Pricing depends on what your business actually needs. A one-location landscaper isn't the same job as a multi-location restaurant. I figure that out on the call — no pressure, no hard sell.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="services__scope-cta">Book a 15-Minute Call &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    padding: 100px 24px;
  }

  .services__container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .services__overline {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--copper-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .services__headline {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .services__intro {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .services__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Base card */
  .services__card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 36px 28px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .services__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Featured card — Full Site */
  .services__card--featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--copper);
  }

  .services__ribbon {
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background-color: var(--copper);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 18px;
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
  }

  .services__card-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* Badge base */
  .services__badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .services__badge--popular {
    background-color: var(--forest);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .services__badge--included {
    background-color: var(--copper);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .services__badge--care {
    background-color: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* Feature list */
  .services__features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .services__features li {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 8px 0;
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(51, 70, 104, 0.08);
  }

  .services__features li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .services__features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--forest);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Tagline for care plan */
  .services__tagline {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding: 0 4px;
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  /* Scope-on-call block (replaces individual price + CTA per card) */
  .services__scope {
    margin-top: 56px;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .services__scope-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .services__scope-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background-color: var(--copper);
    color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--copper);
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .services__scope-cta:hover {
    background-color: var(--navy);
    border-color: var(--navy);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .services__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .services__card--featured {
      order: -1;
    }

    .services__scope {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
